Subject: Cleaning crew
BodyText:
Good morning, all

Just to let everyone know we do have a new cleaning crew starting this week.   If you have any cleaning issues please find them and ask for assistance.

 

 

Thank you,

 

Lisa Henninger

39 Pelham Ridge Dr.

Greenville, SC 29615

864-447-7501

Lisa.Kennedy@tdsynnex.com
